summary: |
    Check that the the c2r inhibits in certain scenario when the firewalld is running
description: |
    On Oracle Linux 8.8 there is an issue with the running firewalld process
    that breaks the conversion. In such case the inhibitor has to be raised.

tier: 0

tag+:
    - firewalld-inhibitor

enabled: false
adjust+:
    - enabled: true
      when: distro == oracle-8
      because: The test case applies to Oracle Linux 8.8

/firewalld_inhibitor:
    tag+:
        - firewalld-inhibitor
    test: |
        pytest -svv -m test_firewalld_inhibitor
